WEBVTT

NOTE
Audio Description captions for the FF8 Opening Credits FMV.
Timestamps were fit to the attached MP4 encode; other versions may need small timing nudges.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Black screen.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:11.200
The SQUARESOFT logo appears on a black background.

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:19.000
The logo fades out to black.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Opening credits appear in white text on black.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:40.000
In stark black-and-white: Squall, a young man with a leather jacket and belts, stands near a chain-link fence.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Low angle: Edea, in a long coat and high boots, strides forward holding a staff.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:01:02.000
More opening credits on black.

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:16.000
A huge full moon hangs over an arched stone structure; the scene feels gothic and still.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:30.000
More opening credits on black.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:37.000
Close-up: a man in a wide-brim hat grips a weapon, his face mostly shadowed.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:45.000
An ornate armored vehicle or carriage glides past, decorated with a sweeping, curving emblem.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:59.000
More opening credits on black.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:15.000
A man drives an open vehicle; the camera focuses on his arms and the steering wheel as scenery passes.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:29.000
More opening credits on black.

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:36.000
A gunblade lies in an open case alongside several rounds of ammunition.

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:43.000
A young woman in a sleeveless outfit stands in bright lights; a long staff or railing cuts across the foreground.

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:58.000
More opening credits on black.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:04.000
A martial artist in a jacket snaps into motion—legs and arms blur in a fast kick or flip.

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:12.000
A stylized emblem fills the frame, like a carved symbol or crest viewed from above.

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:26.000
More opening credits on black.

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:34.000
Two armored figures stand shoulder-to-shoulder on a patterned circular floor, seen from above.

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:47.000
Rinoa is shown from behind in a field of flowers as white feathers drift around her.

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:52.617
The FINAL FANTASY VIII title logo appears on a bright white background.
